{"created": "2026-03-16T20:56:42.043421", "current_version": "1.0.0", "project": "ESP32 Distance Sensor", "versions": {"1.0.0": {"created": "2026-03-16T20:56:42.043419", "creator": {"program": "sphinx_needs", "version": "7.0.0"}, "needs": {"SPEC_ARCH_TASKS_1": {"acceptance_criteria": "", "api_signature": "", "arch": {}, "avatar": null, "closed_at": null, "completion": null, "component": "", "constraints": [], "constraints_error": null, "constraints_passed": true, "constraints_results": {}, "content": "**Description:** Application uses FreeRTOS tasks with priority-based scheduling.\n\n**Task Structure:**\n\n.. code-block:: text\n\n   Core 0: Application Tasks (user-defined)\n   \u251c\u2500\u2500 Main Task (Priority 1)\n   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 Initialization and coordination\n   \u2514\u2500\u2500 User Tasks (Priority varies)\n       \u2514\u2500\u2500 Application-specific logic\n\n   Core 1: WiFi/Network Stack (ESP-IDF managed)\n   \u251c\u2500\u2500 WiFi Management (Priority 2+)\n   \u251c\u2500\u2500 TCP/IP Stack (lwIP)\n   \u2514\u2500\u2500 HTTP Server\n\n**Design Guidelines:**\n\n- Core 0 for application tasks\n- Core 1 reserved for WiFi/network (best performance)\n- Priority range: 0-25 (higher = more important)\n- Monitor stack with ``uxTaskGetStackHighWaterMark()``", "created_at": null, "docname": "12_design/spec_high_level_architecture", "doctype": ".rst", "duration": null, "external_css": "external_link", "external_url": null, "has_dead_links": false, "has_forbidden_dead_links": false, "header_file": "", "id": "SPEC_ARCH_TASKS_1", "id_prefix": null, "is_external": false, "is_import": false, "is_modified": false, "jinja_content": false, "layout": null, "lineno": 368, "links": ["REQ_SYS_ARCH_1"], "links_back": [], "max_amount": null, "max_content_lines": null, "modifications": 0, "parameters": "", "params": null, "parent_need": null, "parent_needs": [], "parent_needs_back": [], "parts": {}, "post_content": null, "post_template": null, "pre_content": null, "pre_template": null, "prefix": null, "priority": "", "query": null, "rationale": "", "returns": "", "section_name": "Threading Architecture", "sections": ["Threading Architecture", "High-Level Architecture Design Specification"], "service": null, "signature": null, "specific": null, "status": "approved", "style": null, "tags": ["threading", "rtos"], "template": null, "title": "FreeRTOS Task Organization", "type": "spec", "type_name": "Design Specification", "updated_at": null, "url": null, "url_postfix": null, "user": null}}, "needs_amount": 1}}}